Class Person

java.lang.Object
core.Person
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Player, Sponsor
public abstract class Person extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a person with basic attributes. This class is abstract and intended to be extended by specific types of persons.
